{"tid":1441592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚防暴警察衝入荃灣綠陽新村攻擊市民","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:07:25.000Z","uid":185730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"016d870d6f1d25954eb542983a2259c63f69ccd9","tid":1441592,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"【哨兵報導綠楊事件】<br />\n有關 2220 綠楊事件原委<br />\n來源：聽過事主第一身講解的街坊覆述<br />\n<br />\n事主是綠楊住客，剛落樓，有3個在m座住的休班警員，截停事主，要查佢身份證<br />\n。<br />\n事主見那3休班警員證不肯俾委任，及裝兇作勢要打佢，於是吹雞找同住綠楊範圍的朋友及街坊支援。<br />\n在對質過程中，有個都係住m座的女人（警察家屬）走落樓時見到就加入，之後女人見勢色唔對就話要報警，之後入咗m座，之後就有防暴來，圍著事主要抄身份證，街坊就起哄，防暴一度衝向街坊，意圖不明，最後過百街坊支援及屌聲，防暴離場，然後街坊把矛頭直指俾防暴入嚟嘅肥佬管理處人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/11/004304_b527e945d3f85afa97f4bd7ab9271c3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F11%2F004304_b527e945d3f85afa97f4bd7ab9271c3e.jpg&h=e5b49a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/11/004324_e564805a47b01c2324be510158cb9f58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F11%2F004324_e564805a47b01c2324be510158cb9f58.jpg&h=4806adbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf06d527edf8ce9b6e91079a31618ca393bc1cc9","tid":1441592,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7661aff3de5c094078d34407153db977f9f332c2","tid":1441592,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"M座狗屋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ba6e4af0d592be095f55bb7024ef2753088cb4","tid":1441592,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"但係如果有人報警係咪啲狗就可以揸正牌入"},{"pid":"a73d4303041169ddb1b90bf29cf8fe09743bf79a","tid":1441592,"uid":69076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"街坊買蛋都驚到凶人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d0f605b38f8bab22a9bf7cf2ae84536b427b3f","tid":1441592,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ba6e4af0d592be095f55bb7024ef2753088cb4","tid":1441592,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"但係如果有人報警係咪啲狗就可以揸正牌入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"應該針對番報警果件狗家屬"},{"pid":"9b3b93069add9ff6323ea20299f78b37f74ea35c","tid":1441592,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}